{"tid":1825454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李家超：香港出現土製炸彈風險高","createTime":"2020-01-15T09:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T10:13:36.000Z","uid":42188,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4920d02229c625f3a74ecd6b4b951ffe209b9acf","tid":1825454,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T09:39:15.000Z","msg":"民建聯陳克勤今天在立法會提出口頭質詢，要求保安局交代3間大學實驗室早前被盜去各類化學品的數量，以及有多少人因盜竊有關化學品而被拘捕及檢控，保安局局長李家超回覆指稱案件仍在調查中，未有數字提供，但他同時指，本地涉及土製炸彈的風險的確較高，指目前要防範本土恐怖主義風險，指過去有5宗案件涉及炸彈，指警方已為逾25個重要供電和水務基礎設施提供保安建議。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講緊少數派既工聯會？</span></span>"},{"pid":"0926217f4fa79a0eb00f8cd8825830186cb24312","tid":1825454,"uid":123774,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T09:40:06.000Z","msg":"工聯會開班授徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6c7ac5007c5faf94e613a146d45dc9f1bc087a","tid":1825454,"uid":158270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T09:41:36.000Z","msg":"梗係高，要炸你班冚家剷吖嘛"},{"pid":"96aa8151d1c512d8e69e2da84007d17b3ba80940","tid":1825454,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T09:42:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1ef731d31fe0fe2e5f85f51bdf43ab6f010e027","tid":1825454,"uid":146737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T09:42:40.000Z","msg":"【第廿貳期牆紙】 為良知發聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1824896/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1824896/page/1</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=bc1912d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\